Simple gallery script.

Data storage in XML files.
Tries to guess gallery structure, if no XML file is given.
Tries to create thumbnail images.

See gallery/example for more details :)
Note! Property "vip" in data.xml files is "Security Through Obscurity"!!!

Please let me know, if you use or modify this script:
 japets miga lv

Project home page:
 http://code.google.com/p/shmiga-gallery/

P.S. change defined properties in gallery.php file if you have to.